src:
Hasil Liga 1: Persela Lamongan vs Barito Putera, Skor Imbang 0-0
04 Nov 2019, 13:58 by Tempo.co, Rina Widiastuti
TEMPO.CO, Jakarta - Persela Lamongan hanya bisa bermain imbang saat menjamu Barito Putera pada pekan ke-27 Liga 1 Indonesia, Senin, 4 November 2019. Bermain di Stadion Surajaya, Kabupaten Lamongan, Jawa Timur, mulai pukul 18.30, kedua tim tak ada satu pun yang berhasil mencetak gol.
Dalam penguasaan bola, kedua tim imbang. Persela yang bermain di hadapan pendukungnya, menciptakan banyak peluang gol. Tembakan yang mengarah ke gawang pun lebih banyak, tetapi tidak ada gol.
Kegagalan tim asuhan Nil Maizar memetik kemenangan, membuat Persela tetap berada di zona degradasi. Saat ini posisinya di urutan ke-16 klasemen sementara Liga 1 2019 dengan 25 poin dari 26 laga.
Sementara Barito Putera saat ini berada di urutan ke-12 dengan 30 poin dari 27 laga.

LIGA INDONESIA
text:
League 1 results: Persela Lamongan vs Barito Putera, Score Score 0-0
04 Nov 2019, 13:58 by Tempo.co, Rina Widiastuti
TEMPO.CO, Jakarta - Persela Lamongan can only draw when entertaining Barito Putera in the 27th week of League 1 Indonesia, Monday, November 4, 2019. Playing at Surajaya Stadium, Lamongan Regency, East Java, starting at 18:30, the two teams were absent none of which scored.
In possession, both teams draw. Persela, who plays in front of his supporters, creates many goal chances. There were more shots on goal, but there were no goals.
The failure of Nil Maizar's side to win, kept Persela in the relegation zone. Currently its position is 16th in the 2019 League 1 standings with 25 points from 26 matches.
While Barito Putera is currently 12th with 30 points from 27 matches.

INDONESIA LIGA
